sub_questions: What is the minimum value in the Release column?
Are all Release values valid years?
What title(s) correspond to the earliest year?

format_notes: Release column contains year values stored as object dtype
May need to convert Release column to numeric for minimum calculation

constraints: Release values should be valid years
Release values should be numeric or convertible to numeric
Result should be a single year value
derived_filters: Exclude rows where Release is null or empty
Exclude rows where Release cannot be converted to a valid year
output_format_requirements: Return the minimum year as a single integer or year value
Optionally include the title associated with that year
